    <summary>A light, fast and secure browser that protects and loves to take care of your privacy and the security of your data.</summary>
    <description>Midori Browser's motto is total privacy, because we don't spy on you, we don't sell invasive advertising, we don't generate profiles of you, because we provide you with tools like a VPN. We give you the best search engine focused on privacy because we don't know anything about you. We say total privacy because you are the owner of your information.

### Features
* **DNS Browsing** - DNS browsing allows safe and extremely fast browsing by blocking many trackers and advertisements. Midori has this option enabled by default.
* **We do not spy on you** - Some browsers spy on your web activity, create profiles and sell user information to make money. Midori does not and never will. Thank you for trusting us.
* **Tracker blocker** - Thanks to the integration of MidoriDNS we can block thousands of trackers in order to protect the privacy and security of our users while surfing the web.
* **Private Tabs** - We have a strong focus on privacy and not only do you have private windows available, you also have private tabs. To guarantee a secure and private browsing experience on Midori.
* **Password manager.** - Securely store your passwords and carry your access with you on your phone, tablets, computers and laptops Midori gives you the ability to fully control your information.
* **Outside Cookie Dialogs** - The dialogs on cookies are tools that allow us to control our privacy on the web, but often becomes annoying, Midori solves this by automating the disappearance of banners.
* **Themes** - Midori consists of thousands of themes that you can download, share and install, Midori gives you a complete customization experience.
* **Toolbars** - Move, hide, delete, and you can edit all the toolbars, with Midori you can do this and much more. The sky is the limit
* **Add-on support** - Extensions are small applications that allow you to extend the functions of the browser. With Midori you have thousands of extensions available.
* **Integration with your OS** - Every operating system is different so Midori has options to change the appearance according to your operating system Windows, Linux &amp; Android soon MacOS and iOS.
* **Augmented Reality** - To personalize your web browsing, with Midori you have the possibility to browse using augmented reality glasses.
* **Total customization - Our commitment is to give you Midori, whatever you want to do you can do, Midori allows you to fully customize the entire browser.
* **Workspaces** - Organize your tabs, divide your workspaces by categories and switch between spaces and environments quickly and instantly.
* **Video pop-out** - With Midori you can play videos while doing other activities, from a floating window and from any position. 
* **Reading mode** - With Midori you can eliminate any distractions while surfing and focus on what you need no advertising or pop-ups.
* **Profile manager** - With Midori users have the possibility to separate their profile and separate all the characteristic information perfect for working environments.
* **Suspended Tabs** - Midori has the ability to suspend hundreds of tabs that you are not using in order to improve resource and power consumption.
* **Tab manager** - Organize all your tabs and get a more organized and efficient navigation, Midori has an advanced tab manager you can do whatever you want.
* **Web Panels** - You can add any website to the sidebar, a great place for social networks, chats, music, videos and more.

